title: My Emojis dont show up and i dont know why
body:
I have a freshly factory reset windows 10 pc and I just clean install League of legends on it and the emojis don't show up and I don't know why 
I even reset the keys in game to see if anything works but NOTHING 

What's wrong??

replies.body: Double check your keybinds in the in-game options really quick to make sure there is still something bound to the emote wheel function. Something might have been reset or not reset properly for it to not work at all anymore.

Yeah i got it 
It was that i was testing them in the practice game and there they dont show up

Btw is there any Diana emoji coming up ???
